An original story by Mallika Duggal. Written November 2018.
The night before Halloween two best friends were talking about their fears. Emily said &ldquo;I&rsquo;m afraid of nothing.&rdquo;
On Halloween night Emily and Lily went trick-or-treating. Lily was shy and curious but Emily was boastful. As they walked a ghost appeared and then disappeared mysteriously. &ldquo;Ahhh!&rdquo; cried Emily but Lily looked curious. &ldquo;What was that?&rdquo; Emily said to Lily. But Lily had disappeared.
